Package: mafTools
Type: Package
Title: A set of functions for processing MAF (Mutation Annotation Format) files.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-29
Author: Anand MT <anand_mt@hotmail.com>
Maintainer: Anand MT <anand_mt@hotmail.com>
Description: Set of functions to get basic stats about a MAF file. Eg; get how many mutations per patient (sample), Classify mutations into Transtions and Transversions, Plot highly mutated genes as matrix,etc.
Depends: ggplot2, plyr, reshape
License: MIT
